    #### Any player

    A player with the #{Constants[Enums.Abilities.PACIFIST]} ability may not perform the following actions:

    * [#{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]}](/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SLAM})
    * [#{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAMBACK]}](/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SLAMBACK}) 
    * [#{Constants[Enums.Actions.SUCKERPUNCH]}](/actions/#{Enums.Actions.SUCKERPUNCH}) 
    * [#{Constants[Enums.Actions.STOMP]}](/actions/#{Enums.Actions.STOMP}) 
    * [#{Constants[Enums.Actions.THROW]}](/actions/#{Enums.Actions.THROW}) the ball at another player's head.

    If a #{Constants[Enums.Actions.THROW]} attempt misses its intended target, it may still accidentally hurt the player in the target hex.
